        <mxCell id="prereg-svc-desc" parent="1" style="text;html=1;fontSize=9;align=center;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#3B82F6;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontFamily=Helvetica;" value="1. createPreRegistration(client_id, email):&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;idempotente — si ya existe PENDING&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;vigente para client_id → reusar&lt;br&gt;2. code = UUID v4 | TTL 30 días | PENDING&lt;br&gt;3. INSERT preregistration (1 por cliente)&lt;br&gt;4. URL: https://preregistro.credibanco.com/&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;registro/{code}&lt;br&gt;5. Invoca Notification_Adapter&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Flujo completo: ver Onboarding_Tarjetahabiente.drawio" vertex="1">
